texts.textentryhtml: Purchased by Patrick J. Kelleher, Graduate School Class of 1947, and Mrs. Marion (Mackie) Kelleher in Luxor at an unknown date from an unknown source; given to the Museum in 1966 by Dr. and Mrs. Kelleher.
